經有新歡, 我仲ON99 期待佢會感動</blockquote><br />\n我諗返起真係好ON9, 我一路剪一路流眼淚,<br />\n原來對方睇都唔想睇, 眼中只有佢既新歡"},{"pid":"9a4d35d9008c3bc7c9b48176841d4e503c4833b8","tid":256174,"uid":15419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"我諗返起真係好委屈, 唉,<br />\n剪左我成晚, 你講句多謝先判我死刑呀"},{"pid":"23cafeaceb0b7e70893a984cb8e32df5ef7d9e58","tid":256174,"uid":14217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:45:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I know that feel <br />\n明明傷害人果個唔係我<br />\n但一直痛苦果個係我</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff363aeeb8fdf12d310afb97e8d205f8c67e11e","tid":256174,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:45:24.000Z","msg":"聽吓四季啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2220284c3b8afd51c19b6dc4655303d1492fc7","tid":256174,"uid":15419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:46:02.000Z","msg":"諗起呢三個月, 佢真係對我好仆街<br />\n我搵幾成日可以唔應機, 咁我當然問下啦:<br />\n我地關係已經唔一樣, 無需要好似以前咁一定要覆你"},{"pid":"a511fc89b23f8a8529744ccda6e3eef52e95b614","tid":256174,"uid":15419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:47:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽吓四季啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n四季係講比人綠帽, 佢無比無我帶, 係分手之後先有新歡"},{"pid":"817d0498ff159265f6ad9d8657b10df158e354c9","tid":256174,"uid":71377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:48:57.000Z","msg":"其實佢有男朋友 判你死刑 先至係最好<br />\n一直拖拖拉拉 繼續傷心 只會更加傷心<br />\n<br />\n回憶的刺 想念痛多一次 只求不相見&hellip;&hellip;（ 嘆氣聲）"},{"pid":"5ee414aae9aab9d87ff2015880ab80d51f197826","tid":256174,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:49:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽吓四季啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n四季係講比人綠帽, 佢無比無我帶, 係分手之後先有新歡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得首歌好有意思<br />\n就算唔係綠唔綠 都係講自己睇開咗同放下果種感覺 就算諗返會流眼淚都唔會有怨恨"},{"pid":"8a9c0b4fe1bbc486db755bfe9ff45608efc3c561","tid":256174,"uid":15419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:51:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢有男朋友 判你死刑 先至係最好<br />\n一直拖拖拉拉 繼續傷心 只會更加傷心<br />\n<br />\n回憶的刺 想念痛多一次 只求不相見&hellip;&hellip;（ 嘆氣聲）</blockquote><br />\n其實我琴日得知佢有新歡後, 我一路等佢親口判我死刑<br />\n然後一直打比佢佢都唔聽, 仲話影響佢生活, 佢有無新歡唔關我事<br />\n係我一直煩佢佢先親口承認<br />\n我就等呢一刻咋"},{"pid":"7f124306f68e1e4406d614850bc92ad2b9a53302","tid":256174,"uid":15419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T11:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽吓四季啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n四季係講比人綠帽, 佢無比無我帶, 係分手之後先有新歡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得首歌好有意思<br />\n就算唔係綠唔綠 都係講自己睇開咗同放下果種感覺 就算諗返會流眼淚都唔會有怨恨</blockquote><br />\n唔知會唔會有一日放底怨恨,<br />\n但我琴日爆到佢咁, 我預左無呢一日"},{"pid":"741da59cdc45ee15c9b623537d8ff9c7d887ae78","tid":256174,"uid":15419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:02:42.000Z","msg":"Tell me you love me<br />\nCome back and haunt me<br />\nOh and I rush to the start<br />\nRunning in circles, chasing our tails<br />\nComing back as we are<br />\n<br />\nNobody said it was easy<br />\nOh it's such a shame for us to part<br />\nNobody said it was easy<br />\nNo one ever said it would be so hard<br />\nI'm going back to the start"},{"pid":"074891945d2860001ceb14187e1cbae00e0d0998","tid":256174,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:04:54.000Z","msg":"聽505 arctic monkeys"},{"pid":"0316f7a956d17b5d0fd3aeddbc2e959e8954c46a","tid":256174,"uid":15419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T12:06:45.000Z","msg"